titles.title: A bill to extend the existing suspension of duty on chemical intermediate.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 7/14/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to extend, through December 31, 1996, the suspension of duty on (6R,7R)-7-amino-3-chloro-8-oxa-5-thia-1-azabicyclo (4.2.0) oct-2-ene-2-carboxylic acid, (4-nitrophenyl)-methyl ester (chemical intermediate).
